A11yPermission.checkBoxText: Tsamaya ka tlhamalalo go ntsha tetla mo sephatlong sa kgwedi mme o se ka wa tlhola o bontsha fensetere eno
A11yPermission.content: Tiro eno e tlhoka tetla ya tiro e e thusang. Fa o batla go letlelela, tsweetswee tobetsa [OK]. Fa o batla go tlogela, tsweetswee tobetsa [Khari].
A11yPermission.title: Kopo ya tumelelo

floatPermission.checkBoxText: Tsamaya ka tlhamalalo go ntsha tetla mo sephatlong sa kgwedi mme o se ka wa tlhola o bontsha fensetere eno
floatPermission.content: Tshebetso ena e hloka tumello ya tshebetso ya fensetere e phaphametseng. Fa o batla go letlelela, tsweetswee tobetsa [OK]. Fa o batla go tlogela, tsweetswee tobetsa [Khari].
